notes:
OpenStreetMap exports for use in GIS applications.

This theme includes all OpenStreetMap features in this area matching:

building IS NOT NULL

Features may have these attributes:

- [name](http://wiki.openstreetmap.org/wiki/Key:name)
- [building](http://wiki.openstreetmap.org/wiki/Key:building)
- [building:levels](http://wiki.openstreetmap.org/wiki/Key:building:levels)
- [building:materials](http://wiki.openstreetmap.org/wiki/Key:building:materials)
- [addr:full](http://wiki.openstreetmap.org/wiki/Key:addr:full)
- [addr:housenumber](http://wiki.openstreetmap.org/wiki/Key:addr:housenumber)
- [addr:street](http://wiki.openstreetmap.org/wiki/Key:addr:street)
- [addr:city](http://wiki.openstreetmap.org/wiki/Key:addr:city)
- [office](http://wiki.openstreetmap.org/wiki/Key:office)

This dataset is one of many [OpenStreetMap exports on
HDX](/dataset?tags=openstreetmap).
See the [Humanitarian OpenStreetMap Team](http://hotosm.org/) website for more
information.
